><quote>you logger-headed and unpolished --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.128" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 128</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you are gallant --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.164" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 2, 164</bibl></cit>.
